 {
  "date": "2014-02-25 11:00", 
  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p583466/", 
  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p583466/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201402/bce07e3b550e4c059a373f1d997f77a9.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">It's hard to believe that New Zealand singer Lorde once referred to Taylor Swift as 'too <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/flawless\" target=\"_blank\">flawless</a> and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unattainable\" target=\"_blank\">unattainable</a>' - because the pair have been acting like&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/inseparable\" target=\"_blank\">inseparable</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">twins recently.</span>很难想象新西兰女歌手洛德曾说泰勒&middot;斯威夫特&ldquo;太过完美&rdquo;&ldquo;难以接近&rdquo;，因为这二位最近像形影不离的双胞胎。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Posting <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/gush\" target=\"_blank\">gushing</a> tributes to each other on Twitter after awards ceremonies is one thing, but posting Instagram <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/snap\" target=\"_blank\">snaps</a> of loving embraces - as Taylor did recently - takes things to a whole new level.</span>颁奖礼之后在推特上互相庆贺恭喜还不足为奇，泰勒最近又把&ldquo;爱的抱抱&rdquo;照片上传Instagram，她可真是把二人关系推到一个新的高度了。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201402/461b73ab4a8b42649c047a9deedad079.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Taylor kept the good <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/vibration\" target=\"_blank\">vibrations</a> alive on Sunday with an Instagram pic of the two of them enjoying a day at the beach.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">泰勒整个星期天心情都不错，在Instagram上传了一张她和洛德在沙滩的照片，看的出来她们很享受。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Turning to smile at the camera - each wearing <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/complementary\" target=\"_blank\">complementary</a> outfits of shorts and skirt, similar blue tops and sunglasses - the two looked like they were shooting <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/promo\" target=\"_blank\">promo</a> photos for an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/impend\" target=\"_blank\">impending</a> girl group.</span>照片中二人回眸一笑，相机记录下精彩瞬间。两个人的穿着也相得益彰，泰勒的短裤配洛德的短裙，相似的蓝色上衣和太阳眼镜，她们两个看上去就像是即将出道的女子组合在拍宣传照一样。</p>\n<p>\n\tTaylor posted the photo on Sunday and kept the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/caption\" target=\"_blank\">caption</a> purposefully vague, by keeping the location a secret and simply writing: 'Bare feet in the sand on a Saturday...'泰勒在星期天上传了这张照片，故意把标题写得含糊不清。她没有写图片拍摄的地点，只是简单地写了一句：&ldquo;周六，赤脚享受沙滩。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\tFair enough. If they are enjoying a close friendship together, the last thing Taylor wants to do is tell her eight-million-plus Instagram followers where to find them.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">其实这很正常，正在共同度过闺蜜相伴的美好时光的时候，泰勒才不会想告诉自己八百多万Instagram粉丝哪里可以找到她们。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">And the idea of them starting a girl group is not as <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/ridiculous\" target=\"_blank\">ridiculous</a> as it sounds.</span>而且她们组团成立一个女子组合这个想法也没有听上去那么荒唐。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201402/54edb722bb3643bb98d2273713b4eb90.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tTaylor's cute picture comes only a couple of days after Lorde spoke on London's Capital FM Radio about a possible collaboration between the two.洛德在伦敦首都之声中坦言她和泰勒可能会有合作，而仅仅几天之后泰勒就上传了那张温馨的合照。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Lorde said that the very fact that their musical styles were so <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/radically\" target=\"_blank\">radically</a> different could be the thing that made working together interesting - and successful.</span>洛德说，正是她和泰勒音乐风格大相径庭，二人合作才会很有趣，而且肯定大获成功。</p>\n<p>\n\tWith record industry money men no doubt dreaming of such a collaboration, what could possibly be stopping these two BFFs getting started?洛德和泰勒这样的合作无疑是唱片业投资人梦寐以求的，还有什么能阻止这对好闺蜜开始她们的合作之旅呢？</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p583466/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p583466\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p582300/\">全球最棒的18个书店：爱书的人绝不能错过</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p583507/\">中国留美学生飙车 洛杉矶上演亡命飞车</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p583450/\">索契冬奥会闭幕式纠错：四环终于变五环</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p580887/\">2013年12月四六级考试沪江网校学员高分榜</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p582896/\">美国女孩西雅图卖煎饼果子 吃货改变世界</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p583467/\">北京雾霾橙色预警 多地空气重度污染持续</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p541220/\">囧研究：早起的鸟儿有虫吃？可不一定！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p582935/\">巴西小镇惊现狼人影像 晚上九点实施宵禁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p579129/\">五个指标助你找到适合自己的公司</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</